        Party A                                     Party B

    Generate Private Key                         Generate Private Key
    (A_priv)                                     (B_priv)

          |                                             |
          |                                             |
          v                                             v

    Generate Public Key                          Generate Public Key
    (A_pub = A_priv * Base Point)                (B_pub = B_priv * Base Point)

          |                                             |
          |                                             |
          v                                             v

    Exchange Public Key                          Exchange Public Key
    (A_pub)                                      (B_pub)

          |                                             |
          |                                             |
          v                                             v

    Calculate Shared Secret                      Calculate Shared Secret
    (Shared Secret = A_priv * B_pub)             (Shared Secret = B_priv * A_pub)

          |                                             |
          |                                             |
          v                                             v

    Derive Shared Secret                          Derive Shared Secret
    (Symmetric Encryption Key)                    (Symmetric Encryption Key)
